snippet.title: Pinball Prelude - Amiga Game
snippet.description:
Amiga game, Pinball Prelude by Effigy 1995

This game was released in different versions to suit various amigas. ocs/ecs/aga chipsets, cdrom/cd32 and even pc version on the same cd.

Im not a fan of this pinball game.  Some nice gfx, but I dont find it fun to play (Its no slamtilt).  The game has 3 tables and this video shows the 3rd table 'Future'  Ive had to use WHDLoad install of the game because the cd cant detect AGA chipset in WinUAE for some odd reason.
